", "peopleAlsoViewed/23/last_name": "Aebi", "peopleAlsoViewed/23/premium": "true", "peopleAlsoViewed/23/profile_picture": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQHfwpSjSiG0GQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/B56ZaAbAhcHUAk-/0/1745911289160?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=LmSmQCdSgnpJuInzImuRkBBnUQZAGg4q4p-x1rLmCL4", "peopleAlsoViewed/23/public_identifier": "urs-aebi-53764432", "peopleAlsoViewed/23/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAbbifsB-01mqC_7N4thpn2-wCgPtvLlX8U", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/entity_urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAgD1KwBWlFOT8PeRZy3SpNB_DeMIpvsdlY", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/first_name": "Graham", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/follower_count": "934", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/headline": "Regional General Manager at Six Senses Hotels Resorts Spas", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/last_name": "Grant", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/premium": "false", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/public_identifier": "graham-grant-6b804939", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAgD1KwBWlFOT8PeRZy3SpNB_DeMIpvsdlY", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/entity_urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWg3fwBHQJo2TD6Ru7R3dCPxydc7h36Z7E", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/first_name": "Frederic", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/follower_count": "5394", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/headline": "Regional General Manager | General Manager | Innovative Leader | Passionate Motivator | \nSkilled Communicator | Service Excellence | \nStrategic Planning | International Experience", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/last_name": "Mazza", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/premium": "false", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/profile_picture": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E03AQGTISngcsi4vA/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1592172240819?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=DRm742LKDEBPmZPQsZIkVLlm5JyS3suDfPqQLUAmjV4", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "fredericmazza", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAWg3fwBHQJo2TD6Ru7R3dCPxydc7h36Z7E", "profilePic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQFroN_rzcWSiQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1703414110286?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=TN__WDqewwQ5GPbi4JLCGU6Ks0rs0_U6HBMpHcCgwUU", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQFroN_rzcWSiQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1703414110286?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=TN__WDqewwQ5GPbi4JLCGU6Ks0rs0_U6HBMpHcCgwUU", "publicIdentifier": "frank-grassmann-80706b22", "recommendations/0/context": "Frank managed Sophie directly", "recommendations/0/date": "September 8, 2021", "recommendations/0/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Sophie for her entire tenure at The Nai Harn. She is well connected and well versed in the luxury segment. She seamlessly blended in the team when she started and was able to make an immediate impact. Looking after Sales, Marketing and Revenue Generation she supervised a sizeable team and was able to get the best out of her people. Her previous exposure to the Asian culture helped her a lot in the Thai environment and made her accomplish her tasks with ease. Under her leadership, the commercial performance to the resort improved year on year. Only a pandemic could stop this growth, otherwise we would have enjoyed continued success. ", "recommendations/0/name": "Sophie Couturier", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Business Development | High End Hospitality | Luxury Industry", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sophcouturier/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACAdzcBA53t7sFb7c2FQgolr-VreqktWvY", "recommendations/1/context": "Frank reported directly to John", "recommendations/1/date": "June 26, 2015", "recommendations/1/description": "When I reported to John he had regional responsibility for 3 properties. He is a very detail oriented and organised manager. He set up - successfully - much needed structure and guidelines. He gave his GMs the necessary freedom operationally to run each resort well, yet he provided the framework for improvements, which were visible both in terms of guest experiences and the financial side. I personally learnt a lot from him. John was able to create an atmosphere of trust and teamwork between us 3 GMs and him as the superior. He also took away certain pressures from the GMs to ensure that we could concentrate on the important things: our guests. He moved on within the company to assume greater responsibilities which he well deserved. ", "recommendations/1/name": "John Philipson", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Senior Luxury Leader specialising in solving problems and driving growth.", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/johnhunterphilipson/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALOknYBh5zBmvacItXZ5MeE03xbK_ITskU", "recommendations/2/context": "Frank managed kevin directly", "recommendations/2/date": "July 23, 2014", "recommendations/2/description": "Kevin is probably the most passionate, creative and hard working Executive Chef I have had the pleasure of working with. I was fortunate that he worked for me for both of my previous assignments. In particular during my last assignment he had the freedom, financial and supervisory support to play out his \"wildest dreams\". He was able to maintain the running operation on the highest standards while at the same time improving and implementing new ideas that quickly became the new standards not only for our property but also the entire group's. His drive to innovate was relentless and he always maintained composure not only to internal but also external customers. Guests were full of praise of Kevin and he was one of the few chefs that I know have a keen interest also outside his kitchen. Hence he was also made in charge of the entire F&B department and had a keen interest in particular in the field of wines. I would not hesitate to work with him again if the opportunity arose. I fully recommend him to any future employer.", "recommendations/2/name": "kevin Fawkes", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Passionate Food & Beverage Specialist I Innovating with Curiosity the Future of Luxury Dinning.", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kevin-fawkes-29693116/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANXR1IBUmBVSKYoW7zoyG7FU3WnWbEp-z0", "recommendations/3/context": "Frank worked with Marisa but on different teams", "recommendations/3/date": "April 7, 2014", "recommendations/3/description": "It was a pleasure working with Marisa during both of our tenures with Soneva Resorts. We worked closely on all matters of Sales & Marketing and I found Marisa a dedicated, hard working, knowledgeable and well connected person. It was because of her that the performance of both properties under her supervision has improved greatly and she was able to push through many new initiatives which will be visible and bear fruit for years to come. She was able to put her stamp firmly on Soneva and hope that one day we can work again together.", "recommendations/3/name": "Marisa Aranha", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Leadership in Hospitality / Business growth and transformation / Sales & Distribution / Brand Marketing and Innovation", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/marisaaranha/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAVXaUwBMxPc-oQ8pNZxVLlRQaiWPJPvOmA", "recommendations/4/context": "Frank was Kurt's client", "recommendations/4/date": "May 8, 2012", "recommendations/4/description": "Kurt has designed and implemented our water purification plant (also known as the Six Senses Drinking Water plant). His expertise was always very much appreciated as well as his loyal support and after-sales-service.", "recommendations/4/name": "Kurt Apel", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "CEO Eco Pure Thailand - Eco Pure Maldives, Vietnam, www.eco-purity.com", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kurt-apel-b8443a4b/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAqQnRQBxU12T76NWTHmeagVn9A6xdxhCO0", "recommendations/5/context": "Frank was senior to Inge but didn't manage Inge directly", "recommendations/5/date": "May 8, 2012", "recommendations/5/description": "Inge was initially recruited at the resort in order to assist our Spanish speaking guests. Very quickly she established herself as a very capable host at the front office and throughout her tenure with us she did an outstanding job which led to subsequent promotions within our company.", "recommendations/5/name": "Inge B.", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Founder and GM of GUT Kombucha", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/inge-becker/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALfMXsBjJmX7Ux9B1kLGAznkc_UKZG0Ep8", "recommendations/6/context": "Frank managed Naiyana directly", "recommendations/6/date": "February 2, 2012", "recommendations/6/description": "Khun Naiyana is probably the most complete and professional financial controller I have worked with so far. She possess a full understanding of her area of expertise that stretches even beyond an FC's usual responsibilities. She is strict, following policies and procedures, yet has an understanding of operational necessities and cooperates for the greater good of the company. It is a pleasure working with her.", "recommendations/6/name": "Naiyana Rattanothai", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Financial Controller at COMO Point Yamu", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/naiyana-rattanothai-6087a344/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAlfFagBCErXoGgYYsC_74qV89p8KvE_nkQ", "recommendations/7/context": "Frank reported directly to Alasdair", "recommendations/7/date": "December 14, 2011", "recommendations/7/description": "I have always appreciated Alasdair's deep operational knowledge. At the same time he displays strong financial and entrepreneurial skills. In his role as COO he knows what he wants and is always clear in communicating goals and objectives to his GMs. He is very well organised and uses technology efficiently to help him manage the workload. Alasdair always finds the right balance between driving the organisation and goals forward and at the same time supporting his subordinates to ensure that goals are achieved. Alasdair is well-liked in the organisation and it is a pleasure to work with him.", "recommendations/7/name": "Alasdair Junor", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Managing Director at The Private office", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alasdairjunor/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJMYCQBL3qr_rwHEdeV10ZpZ5b--S8oJBM", "recommendations/8/context": "Frank was senior to Monika but didn't manage Monika directly", "recommendations/8/date": "November 29, 2010", "recommendations/8/description": "Monika was a tremendous asset to the resort. Her in depth knowledge, passion, commitment and constant drive to excel was second to none and I have yet to have met any sommelier as good as her.", "recommendations/8/name": "Monika Bielka-Vescovi", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Founder, Napa Wine Class | CEO, MBV Wine Media | Wine Educator (WSET 1-Diploma) | VP of Education, National Director of Marketing Women for WineSense I IMW Stage 2", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/monika-bielka-vescovi-232780/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAdHUYB7qp3yPF0xAOhgmS92wQFZYRQOyI", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "John managed Frank directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "June 23, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I worked with Frank for many years in his capacity as General Manager at Evason Phuket in Thailand. \n\nFrank was instrumental in turning the businesses around. He is a very dynamic leader with great creativity and a hands on approach which made him well liked by his team, his staff and his owners. He was quick to adapt and able to bring about change and better business performance and standards with enthusiasm.\n\nFrank is commercially astute, analytical and is a seasoned operator.\n\nHe is an exemplary character and is well trusted and respected.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "John Philipson", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Senior Luxury Leader specialising in solving problems and driving growth.", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/johnhunterphilipson/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALOknYBh5zBmvacItXZ5MeE03xbK_ITskU", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Antony managed Frank directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "August 2, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I had the great pleasure to work with Frank for a number of years and always appreciated his calm personality and mature approach. Frank handles pressure very well and did a great job of managing Soneva Kiri under some difficult situations.\nAs a General Manager, Frank is a good all rounder and especially excels in Finance, sales and all matters to do with food and beverage.\nFrank gains huge respect from his Teams due to his professionalism and his no nonsense approach.\nFrank is a highly experienced Manager and a natural Leader", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Antony Paton  FIH", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Cluster General Manager at Soneva Maldives", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/antony-paton-fih-a6034b18/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAOcOCgBvDV5o039JIus0LaxAMYJh7wx4_E", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Gerhard was Frank's client", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "November 22, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Frank was instrumental in planning/executing the renovation and subsequent rebranding of Dusit Thani Manila. He was results-orientated and customer-focused and well-liked by his co-workers.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Gerhard Kropp", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "President at Philippine Hotelier Inc", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gerhard-kropp-2599066/", "recommendationsR