n for his craft. He is dedicated, highly reliable, and consistently willing to go the extra mile to ensure both quality and guest satisfaction. His calm leadership and strong organisational skills make him a dependable presence in the kitchen, even during high-pressure service.\n\nHe successfully led the “Beach Bar & Grill” at Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort, maintaining high culinary standards while ensuring smooth day-to-day operations. Beyond that, Bram regularly supported our other restaurants and kitchens, demonstrating versatility and a strong team mindset. He also played a key role in large-scale events, contributing to the successful execution of functions for up to 500 guests with precision and consistency.\n\nBram is not only technically skilled but also committed, proactive, and solutions-oriented. Any hotel and culinary team would benefit greatly from his expertise, strong work ethic, ability to work both within and lead a team, and consistently positive attitude.\n\nI highly recommend him.", "recommendations/0/name": "Bram Scheidmann", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Hello my name is Bram Scheidmann, I am a chef from the Netherlands, i specialize in western cuisine, i am a real team player and I am very passionate about my job!", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bram-scheidmann-486251293/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAEcMpmYBccsudc4xtf1_dMiA346RmTo0XSI", "recommendations/1/context": "Urs worked with Kanyapat (Belle) on the same team", "recommendations/1/date": "May 22, 2025", "recommendations/1/description": "I had the pleasure of welcoming Khun Belle to the Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort as part of her journey in the Dusit International & Resort Lead Management Trainee program. Her time with us was a component of her training, and from the very beginning, she impressed me with her open-mindedness, eagerness to learn, and willingness to be involved in all aspects of the operation.\n\nShe approached every task and assignment with a positive attitude, quickly becoming a valued member of our team. Whether on the floor or behind the scenes, Khun Belle was hands-on, engaged, and fully committed—always ready to go the extra mile. Her approachable nature and can-do spirit made her a joy to work with. She was not only appreciated by the team but also demonstrated excellent guest relations and interpersonal skills.\n\nI’m confident that Khun Belle has a bright future ahead of her, and I wholeheartedly recommend her for any role that values commitment, adaptability, and a strong sense of teamwork.", "recommendations/1/name": "Kanyapat (Belle) Leongamta", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Lead Management Trainee at Dusit Thani Dubai", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kanyapat-belle-leongamta-248062306/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAE32VNgB5j5CSqZc_95wKmuq9PRpDaA1s1U", "recommendations/2/context": "Urs worked with Julian on the same team", "recommendations/2/date": "August 8, 2022", "recommendations/2/description": "I had the pleasure to have Julian in the team at Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort. Julian was an awesome Front Office Manager! \n\nHe is a real pleasure to work with and has excellent expertise in front office and hotel operation management, leadership, and guest relation. He has a very strong work ethic and excellent problem-solving abilities. \n\nJulian leads by example, is hands-on, result-driven, and works towards maximal guest satisfaction, profitably while driving associate engagement. He is not only a reliable and forward-thinking manager but also an inspiring team player. \n\nI enjoyed working with Julian and highly recommend him!", "recommendations/2/name": "Julian Bruno", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "General Manager I Passionate Hotelier I Hotel Operations I Pre-Opening", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/julian-bruno-246671137/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACFhNxYBfoBfOwp3qa9kC9OJow0CZabAtDc", "recommendations/3/context": "Urs managed Chanisa directly", "recommendations/3/date": "June 15, 2022", "recommendations/3/description": "I tremendously enjoy working with K. Chanisa at Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort. Khun Chanisa is a passionate, forward-thinking hospitality leader with excellent people, operational, and management skills. She deeply cares about associates, guests, partners and the interests of the company. She is loyal, dedicated, trustworthy, result-driven, and always willing to assist and to take on more responsibilities. Khun Chanisa is highly capable and will be an asset to any hotel as a leader. She earns my highest recommendation.", "recommendations/3/name": "Chanisa Bunsuwan", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Resort Manager at dusitD2 Feydhoo Maldives", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chanisa-bunsuwan-7859a335/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAdxfpUBDBNlECHcCTQAEINGrlkaoVazorI", "recommendations/4/context": "Urs worked with Patrick on the same team", "recommendations/4/date": "October 31, 2021", "recommendations/4/description": "Patrick is fantastic to work with. He is a talented, passionate, creative, and hands-on Executive Chef with a very positive attitude towards work. After Patrick assumed the Executive Chef position in Layana Resort & Spa, he adapted quickly to the new environment and was inspiring and motivating his colleagues. Thanks to his expertise and dedication, he is able to drive associate engagement, guest satisfaction while achieving demanding cost and revenue objectives. \n\nI will always hold Patrick in the highest esteem and I absolutely recommend him.", "recommendations/4/name": "Patrick Vitti", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Director of Food & Beverage at Minor Hotels | Anantara Bophut Koh Samui", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/patrick-vitti-a2a600b1/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABfCncIBAQAVxW_bD6bQMEVfJoV8pTFw3yw", "recommendations/5/date": "October 31, 2021", "recommendations/5/description": "Under Ansgar's leadership, Layana Resort & Spa received numerous prestigious awards, including TripAdvisor's 1st Place Top Hotel in Thailand and 1st Place Top Hotel for Romance in Asia.\n\nI had the pleasure of working with Ansgar since he joined Layana Resort & Spa as General Manager. I was always impressed by Ansgar's ability to develop and execute new ideas and concepts in his pursuit to find new ways to evolve and grow the business. Ansgar is forward-thinking, dedicated, trustworthy, takes ownership of the property, and invests himself deeply in hotel operations. He is entrepreneurial and is getting things done. \n\nThanks to Ansgar, Layana Resort & Spa was further enhancing its facilities and services, attracting new market segments, resulting in positive results in all areas. \n\nAs General Manager, Ansgar will be an asset to any hotel and as a leader, earns my highest recommendation.", "recommendations/5/name": "Ansgar Schlemmer", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "General Manager | Luxury & Destination Hotels | Driving Operational Excellence, Guest Satisfaction & Revenue Growth | Hospitality Executive Leader", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ansgar-schlemmer-51a61662/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA1C5GYBBi3tAyoDs1adR436DoVmJOssekQ", "recommendations/6/context": "Urs managed Paul directly", "recommendations/6/date": "November 2, 2020", "recommendations/6/description": "Thanks to Paul, Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort is the well-being leader in Krabi.\n\nI was hiring Paul two years ago when I was looking for a fitness and wellness expert capable to develop a best-in-class fitness and wellness program, including fitness and wellness retreats. In the two years I have worked with Paul, I’ve seen him not only excel at the core elements of his job assignments – like developing, implementing, marketing and constantly enhancing our Premium Fitness & Wellness Retreats – but also take on other tasks and projects, well beyond the scope of his role, like menu development, and even championing our demanding Junior Klong Muang Swimming project. \n\nUnder Paul’s leadership, guest experience scores, financial performance and the team’s engagement and performance have all improved. \n\nAs a fitness and wellness expert and as a leader, Paul earns my highest recommendation.", "recommendations/6/name": "Paul Reynolds", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Fitness, Health & Wellness Professional", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulreyno/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA0H0zsBnIKAZ32Xqho2sgwOeiKdH7zr8NI", "recommendations/7/context": "Urs was senior to Cedric  but didn't manage Cedric  directly", "recommendations/7/date": "February 8, 2019", "recommendations/7/description": "Cedric is a pleasure to work with, and has exceptional guest relation and F&B skills. He is professional, hands-on, dedicated and passionate and able to look after the most demanding guests. Cedric would be an asset to any team, and we are fortunate to have him at one of our hotels. ", "recommendations/7/name": "Cedric  Veith ", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Wine lover, spirits professional, relationship builder, hospitality focused, internationally experienced", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cedric-veith-c136686/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAPDoG8BGZ6L-rvEhEnrM_NNNJROkA4AhQI", "recommendations/8/context": "Urs managed Pichet directly", "recommendations/8/date": "November 9, 2017", "recommendations/8/description": "I had the pleasure to have worked with Khun Pichet for the past three years at Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort. Khun Pichet has consistently been a very strong executive, valued by co-workers and the team. His communication and people skills are excellent. Further, Khun Pichet is motivated and willing to learn and extend his expertise. He has passion, drive and is able to implement his innovative ideas in a professional and effective manner. \n\nAlso, it is a pleasure to work with him. Khun Pichet is very committed, has a positive “can-do” attitude and is always available to lend a hand to co-workers when necessary. I highly recommend Khun Pichet; he would be an asset and add value to any hotel and organization and hope I have the pleasure to work with him again in the future. ", "recommendations/8/name": "Pichet Pongsirisukbhinya", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Hotel Manager I Krabi I Thailand", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pichet-pongsirisukbhinya-72488363/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA16MEwBHd0rLhTEIpZjq2cn_VYu4G22HMM", "recommendations/9/context": "Urs was senior to Aljoscha but didn't manage Aljoscha directly", "recommendations/9/date": "August 25, 2017", "recommendations/9/description": "It was a delight working with Aljoscha who I experienced as a hard working, very organized hospitality professional during his time as Assistant F&B Manager here at the Dusit Thani Krabi. I was impressed by his creativity and ambition facing various tasks such as the reopening and rebranding of two of our bars and our Italian restaurant. His proactive attitude in daily operation and towards challenging projects highly contributed to the development of our F&B department. His professional service mind with a “hands-on” attitude positively affected the overall team performance and his highly cost focused approach made him a great asset to our company. I hope to have the opportunity working with Aljoscha again and until then can highly recommend him.", "recommendations/9/name": "Aljoscha H.", "recommendations/9/subtitle": "Sales | Planning | Analytics", "recommendations/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/aljoschahamp/", "recommendations/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABGSOT0BdpghiMQgZVr_IO2wkRAWGT_2TgI", "recommendations/10/context": "Urs was senior to Chanachan but didn't manage Chanachan directly", "recommendations/10/date": "May 24, 2017", "recommendations/10/description": "Khun Chanachan and worked together at Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort, where he was Sales Coordinator Events and I was General Manager. Khun Chanachan is talented, hard-working, hands-on and a pleasure to work with. He has a very positive and can-do attitude and contributed greatly to the success of our resort and the events/sales team. Highly recommended!\n\n", "recommendations/10/name": "Chanachan Intaraprom", "recommendations/10/subtitle": "Assistant Sales Manager at Westin Hotels & Resorts", "recommendations/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chanachan-intaraprom-aa1695127/", "recommendations/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB8_ONkBOrSsuWkuqwef86dfs9chggMxRwc", "recommendations/11/context": "Urs managed Linda directly", "recommendations/11/date": "September 13, 2014", "recommendations/11/description": "I has been a great pleasure to work with Linda at Sheraton Davos: She is an exceptional Front Office Manager. She is energetic, accurate, extremely organised, dependable, guest focused, and (also important) possesses a wonderful sense of humour. Further, Linda is able to work with all Starwood systems and tools in a professional and effective manner.\n\nIn addition, Linda has passion, drive and is able to follow through to ensure that the job gets done. She is flexible and willing to work on any project that is assigned to her. \n\nI recommend Linda without hesitation and hope I am able to work with her again in the future.", "recommendations/11/name": "Linda Staag (Stag)", "recommendations/11/subtitle": "Leitung Mountain Resorts (Hotel Waldhuus Davos & Mountain Plaza Hotel)", "recommendations/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/linda-staag-stag-25907759/", "recommendations/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAxKN6UBKJ2zgfW6J5K2j6ED7AK3mTLFdt8", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Urs was senior to Bram but didn't manage Bram directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "February 27, 2026", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I would like to share my appreciation for Urs Lienhard as a Regional Manager. Urs is an exceptionally professional leader who consistently demonstrates integrity, competence, and strong decision-making skills. He approaches every situation with clarity and confidence, creating a stable and motivating work environment.\n\nWhat truly sets Urs apart is his open-mindedness. He actively listens to different perspectives, values input from his team, and encourages constructive dialogue. This makes team members feel respected and heard, which strengthens collaboration and overall performance.\n\nOn a personal level, Urs is genuinely kind and approachable. He maintains a positive attitude and treats everyone with fairness and respect. His leadership style balances professionalism with empathy, making him not only an effective manager but also a great person to work with.\n\nI am grateful to have worked to have worked with him and would highly recommend him as a strong Manager", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Bram Scheidmann", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Hello my name is Bram Scheidmann, I am a chef from the Netherlands, i specialize in western cuisine, i am a real team player and I am very passionate about my job!", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bram-scheidmann-486251293/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAEcMpmYBccsudc4xtf1_dMiA346RmTo0XSI", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Kanyapat (Belle) worked with Urs on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "May 22, 2025", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "During my Lead Management Trainee journey at Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort, I had the privilege of learning under the leadership of RGM Urs.\n\nHe is an exceptionally friendly and approachable leader—someone you can comfortably speak with about anything, both professional and personal. His open-door approach created a positive and inclusive environment where everyone felt respected and heard.\n\nWhat stood out most was his strong work ethic, forward-thinking mindset, and ability to inspire through innovation and vision. He consistently led by example and worked to elevate both the guest experience and the team’s growth.\n\nI’m truly grateful for the opportunity to learn from him. His leadership left a lasting impression and set a high benchmark for what it means to be an inspiring Regional General Manager.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Kanyapat (Belle) Leongamta", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Lead Management Trainee at Dusit Thani Dubai", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kanyapat-belle-leongamta-248062306/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAE32VNgB5j5CSqZc_95wKmuq9PRpDaA1s1U", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Chanisa reported directly to Urs", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "February 27, 2024", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "It is with great pleasure that I recommend Khun Urs Lienhard, my former boss and the Regional General Manager at Dusit Thani Krabi. During my tenure as his number 2, I had the privilege of witnessing firsthand Khun Urs's exceptional leadership qualities, innovative mindset, and unwavering dedication to achieving results.\n\nKhun Urs possesses a remarkable talent for effective management, consistently demonstrating the ability to navigate complex challenges with ease. His strategic vision and forward-thinking approach have been instrumental in driving the success of our organization. Khun Urs's innovative ideas and projects to enhance the property and service offerings have set new standards of excellence within the industry.\n\nOne of Khun Urs's most admirable traits is his commitment to supporting and guiding his team members. As a mentor, he invests time and effort in nurturing talent, providing valuable insights, and empowering individuals to reach their full potential. His approachable nature and genuine interest in the professional development of his team have fostered a culture of collaboration and growth.\n\nFurthermore, Khun Urs is undeniably result-driven, consistently setting high standards and inspiring others to strive for excellence. Under his leadership, our team achieved remarkable outcomes, exceeding targets and delivering exceptional performance.\n\nIn conclusion, Khun Urs Lienhard is an outstanding leader, mentor, and results-driven professional. His managerial acumen, innovative spirit, guidance, and support have left an indelible mark on our organization. I am honored to have had the opportunity to work alongside him and wholeheartedly endorse him for any leadership role he may pursue in the future.\n", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Chanisa Bunsuwan", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Resort Manager at dusitD2 Feydhoo Maldives", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chanisa-bunsuwan-7859a335/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAdxfpUBDBNlECHcCTQAEINGrlkaoVazorI", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Pruetha reported directly to Urs", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "November 9, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Khun Urs is a highly skilled and knowledgeable manager. He is friendly, helpful, also goes above and beyond to maintain the team spirit. He is such an inspiration for me, and I feel proud to have worked under his guidance.”", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Pruetha Wongwean", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "General Manager", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pruetha-wongwean-6bb581132/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACB57q8BS9MROS6Zg1W_sqGqNi-bfL9IvTU", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "David reported directly to Urs", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "August 13, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "I started my work journey with Urs in Thailand. I had the pleasure to work with him for several organizations and positions for many years. He is an outstanding mentor. I learned a lot from Urs as a person and a leader. He taught me many valuable lessons on life and he helped me to grow as a young hotelier. He leads by example and I improved in many areas thanks to him.\n\nHe brings integrity, hardworking and dedication to his work. He has a large expertise and knowledge in the hospitality field. A driven-results, guest oriented and efficient hotelier who made many projects possible such as for example the successful rebranding of the Dusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort in 2015. His ability to develop new ways to exceed the guests’ expectations were always both motivating and inspiring. He is also a broad-minded leader who welcomes changes and new ideas. He is highly adaptable and worked with people from different backgrounds. \n\nHe earned everybody respects through his skills, work ethics and values within the several organizations where we worked together. It is a real pleasure to know Urs and I am lucky that I work with him.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "David Caille", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Executive Assistant Manager ∣ Operations at Minor Hotels", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/david-caille-ab303041/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAi5iScB4Hc4NAE2iFbxtJYKESZPNfztqVw", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Paul reported directly to Urs", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "October 27, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "I could safely say that Urs is worthy of the title \"the best boss\" i have ever worked with. Urs is a dynamic leader who is forward thinking and relentless in his pursuit to find new ways to evolve and grow your business. A leader who cares about his associates and the interests of the company. A project leader who has the determination and drive to envision new ideas, bring them to fruition and see them through to the end, Urs had the ingredients necessary to put the people together and guide them towards completion of the end goal. I personally always felt supported as a HOD in my efforts to do the best for the company and my loyalty was returned. I have also personally learn't a lot and have gained a lot of new experience working with Urs who was always open to share that rich knowledge and experience to help you do your best.\n\nI can only hope that my next boss is as likable, charismatic, professional and experienced as Urs.\n\nPaul Reynolds\nFitness & Wellness Manager\nDusit Thani Krabi Beach Resort \nSep 2018 - Oct 2020", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Paul Reynolds", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Fitness, Health & Wellness Professional", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/paulreyno/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA0H0zsBnIKAZ32Xqho2sgwOeiKdH7zr8NI", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Ansgar reported directly to Urs", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "April 6, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "I have worked with Urs at MBK Hotel & Tourism for a number of years. I appreciated his charisma, his intelligence in decision taking, his coolness but mixed with enthusiasm and self-motivation at all times. I see Urs as a great true inspiring leader, hotelier and colleague.\nI hope our career paths will always cross again.", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Ansgar Schlemmer", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "General Manager | Luxury & Destination Hotels | Driving Operational Excellence, Guest Satisfaction & Revenue Growth | Hospitality Executive Leader", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ansgar-schlemmer-51a61662/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA1C5GYBBi3tAyoDs1adR436DoVmJOssekQ", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Urs was senior to Cedric  but didn't manage Cedric  directly", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "February 8, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "I have the pleasure to work with Urs for the MBK Hospitality Management Group, his the go-to person for any advice or problem-solving. \n\nUrs, is creative, innovative and aiming for a high level of success for each Hotel development under his expertise. \n  \nI would highly recommend him for he maintains and constantly brings new ideas to the table of the Hotel Operations.\n\n\n\n", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Cedric  Veith ", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Wine lover, spirits professional, relationship builder, hospitality focused, internationally experienced", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cedric-veith-c136686/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAPDoG8BGZ6L-rvEhEnrM_NNNJROkA4AhQI", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Pichet reported directly to Urs", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "November 10, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "Ok It is my pleasure to warmly recommend Khun Urs . I have known Khun Urs for over three years. He was instrumental in the successful and professional rebranding from Sheraton to Dusit in April 2015. Khun Urs leads by example, is innovative, proactive and result oriented; he was always ready to put all his energy and tome to get the job done. Besides his operational and project expertise, he also possesses deep knowledge in Digital and and Social Media Marketing. It is a pleasure to work with Khun Urs and I highly recommended him", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Pichet Pongsirisukbhinya", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Hotel Manager I Krabi I Thailand", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pichet-pongsirisukbhinya-72488363/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA16MEwBHd0rLhTEIpZjq2cn_VYu4G22HMM", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Ana Luiza reported directly to Urs", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "April 24, 2017", "recommendations